data.text:
Property Description

Access Pigeon Forge and Gatlinburg attractions without fighting the traffic! This property has lots of possibilities . . . overnight rental, long-term rental, vacation property. Each unit has 2 bedrooms and 2 full baths, large master suite, wood burning fireplace in living room, vaulted ceilings, laundry area, and ample parking. Both units are currently rented, providing an opportunity for immediate income on your investment. As with all Real Estate transactions, Buyer(s) should verify all information independently including HOA info & Square Footage, Buy title insurance, have a survey, home inspection, and all other needed inspections. Most information from Tax records and not verified by listing agent/Company. HOA information should be verified independently.
